{"tid":2304636,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭月娥：通識科改革是回應社會關懷青年成長的意見","createTime":"2020-11-29T03:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T04:39:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54f8578a8b18715923072844a53a596f4fc0e749","tid":2304636,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥出席電視節目時表示，再講到有關通識科改革，她指通識科自推出以，爭議不斷，外界有正反意見，包括有家長感到擔心，認為教科書及題目偏離了客觀持平，今次改革是回應社會關懷青年成長的意見。<br />\n<br />\n她強調，本港教育制度屬香港內部事務，同中央無直接關係，亦非收到中央命令而要改革通識科。林鄭月娥說，通識科日後仍可以有時事討論，但就應該要有基礎，例如要討論「違法達義」，就應該先向學生講解守法意識及法律基礎。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2368473&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR%2F4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=8888af80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368473</a>"},{"pid":"24634332e541c90a7eb6df99b85e358d7a0864cf","tid":2304636,"uid":76804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"次次中共想做既野就話回應社會意見<br />\n佢既社會=中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6076a7bf5e838e430061fde93fa0916108900fd0","tid":2304636,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:57:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50ba4fc0ffc2d57d2521ce4a860a3ff3092da3b9","tid":2304636,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"24634332e541c90a7eb6df99b85e358d7a0864cf","tid":2304636,"uid":76804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"次次中共想做既野就話回應社會意見<br />\n佢既社會=中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:39:00.000Z","msg":"隨便9 UP一樣野就當係理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}